[{"Code":"en","Title":"How payment links work","Slug":"how-payment-links-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote data-block-id=\"mji4bgnp-jbpq3y-208\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\" style=\"background:rgb(221, 247, 255);border-left:4px solid rgb(0, 106, 138);overflow:auto;\"><p data-block-id=\"mji4bgnq-3jtyq7-209\">This is legacy product and will be deprecated in the future. Use our new <a href=\"/v1/docs/how-payment-sessions-work#payment-link\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Payment Session product</a> instead and see our <a href=\"/v1/docs/migrate-to-payment-session\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">migration guide page here</a> if you are existing Payment Links/Invoice merchants.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"e1512a76-7ca5-4d5b-a248-afb55369799c\">Payment Links offer a simple, no-code solution for businesses to collect payments with ease. Our product enhances the payment experience for your customers, making them ideal for businesses looking for an optimized checkout experience while maintaining a cost-effective integration.</p><p data-block-id=\"mjjlcyf1-5rrbzr-033\"></p><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"mjjla4dw-1tjtic-006\"><strong>Private notes</strong></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"900\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:900px;width:900px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"mjjlabbw-imz14w-009\"><strong>Product</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbw-x13dyi-010\"><strong>Single Payment Link</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbx-s6w07z-011\"><strong>Multiple Payment Link</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbx-bcpwbq-012\"><strong>Batch Payment Link</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbx-gkk1zm-013\">Description</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbx-bkikix-014\">One payment link to accept a single payment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbx-ovmzp5-015\">One payment link to accept multiple payments</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbx-o4yynn-016\">Create multiple payment links in bulk using CSV file</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabby-7gq2fr-017\">No-code solution</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabby-4njeg2-018\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabby-1ase0j-019\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabby-yrtulw-020\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabby-2zf0lj-021\">API integration</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabby-kurt48-022\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbz-mxf15v-023\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">❌</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbz-tjipk0-024\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">❌</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbz-xi93c6-025\">Amount required</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbz-81ql4f-026\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbz-s5nuiu-027\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">❌</emoji> (optional—end user can define the amount on our Checkout UI)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabbz-sr4rj3-028\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabc0-asho4i-029\">Best use case</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabc0-66s1rz-030\">One-off payments (e.g., e-commerce orders)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mjjlabc0-2f795j-031\">Open static link for multiple payments (e.g., donations, fundraising)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"mjjlabc0-60cknu-032\">Bulk invoicing, organizing payments for multiple customers</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><p data-block-id=\"mjjla4dw-euzlzp-008\"></p><p data-block-id=\"a47fe000-71d7-42bd-98fc-ea9df48f05c0\"><em>Actual user interface for reference</em></p><p data-block-id=\"ee8a3f7d-165d-4e01-9908-70d8145a1e73\"><img data-block-id=\"7c6f058b-a6e7-487f-aea3-9e4d8c3ff754\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(18).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(18).png\" width=\"902\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:902px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"0ce1e7f3-705b-439d-b98f-9ed60cd190ca\">Solutions</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"4c5bb93d-cfc7-4e4e-b0a9-d717479bfa7f\">No-code solution</h3><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"08bbccdf-ccd7-422f-b826-a2bd93b8d44d\">Using a simple guided interface on the Xendit Dashboard, you can create payment links without any technical knowledge. Xendit also support delivery of payment links via email and WhatsApp to your customers. Alternatively, you can share these links through any communication channel of your choice.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c11bda4f-32c6-4130-bb86-24fa26b2aa5d\">Follow these steps to create a Payment Link using the Xendit Dashboard:</p><ol data-block-id=\"4ef2203e-0eb7-42bb-a2c1-6519929cfd26\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c7a5022d-adf6-4c2a-964a-dbc59eb0f434\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c7c46c3a-7e2d-419f-b5cc-78f18a99589b\">Go to the <strong>Payment Links</strong> page on your dashboard</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c8f5551f-1dcc-4edb-82e8-6c2d7651ae16\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"63669e41-9203-453e-b2f6-3f0dd3374789\">Click <strong>Create Payment Link</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"14ab08ce-d02e-448a-95f9-47b4ca1fed3a\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"72ba3b23-b9e7-4a23-ba6d-e6b1266b5791\">Fill in the <strong>payment details</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"468e0f44-a891-4d39-a1fa-05b3441d4af9\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"dbfc4944-cb39-4d7e-b14d-143bfc6f7995\">(Optional) Leave the amount blank for donations or multiple payment link</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1c2fd757-e039-441b-9fa6-506062b74015\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1a870861-d2de-49c3-910f-4191e105e54e\">(Optional) Configure customer details and notification channels</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"39e5a41a-a45d-489e-9f66-31662ad01afe\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c3e5403f-8b4e-4eb5-8e52-43f50381f53d\">Click <strong>Create Payment Link</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"42c2f66d-1f37-4442-b676-872da50e3d82\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"3b80d47d-d361-4b31-9ea7-e736a4fb2e57\"><strong>Share the link</strong> with your customers to redirect them to the Xendit-hosted checkout page</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"9a9218c5-dc6c-4eb6-94b9-e8596ad1e2cf\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"a23c52ca-c410-4362-bfa1-ac568358f6e5\">Monitor payments via email notifications or generate a report for status updates</p></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"387e6a7a-9df3-45aa-8232-f9e690f1753f\">API integration</h3><p data-block-id=\"c120054d-f922-42b0-8901-bb0d9be7eff2\">If you have a more complex use case that requires your system to create payment links dynamically, our product is also available via an API-based integration. This integration method allows you to sync up your order management system to our hosted payments collection system. <a href=\"/v1/docs/payment-links-api-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">You can find our detailed integration guides here</a>.   </p><h4 data-block-id=\"71e69fd0-833e-4aca-8f52-c7e4ae39972e\">How it works</h4><h4 data-block-id=\"fad075e9-7dbe-4fcc-897c-31124a5d31d9\">Endpoints</h4><ol data-block-id=\"1324f69f-7fd8-4fc2-96d8-c9e83682b04b\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"777546fd-fd58-418d-9a01-cafd85b3920e\"><p data-block-id=\"bd93ab85-0735-48b2-b3b2-c5c8dad1f107\"><code>v2/invoices</code> - to generate payment links with minimal lines of code.</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"b6b5de88-efa9-432a-9a94-48a2a6cf48fb\">Creating a payment link</h4><p data-block-id=\"f3770f52-937a-4449-bc1b-db4d196ed70d\">Example API request payload:</p><pre data-block-id=\"2d80317b-6930-4713-b504-f590b13498d5\" language=\"json\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{  \"external_id\": \"payment-link-example\",\n  \"amount\": 100000,\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Air Conditioner\",\n      \"quantity\": 1,\n      \"price\": 100000,\n      \"category\": \"Electronic\",\n      \"url\": \"https://yourcompany.com/example_item\"\n    }\n  ]\n}</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"caf6e6c8-4c08-40b0-85f9-03548fb22964\">The API response includes a URL that you can use to redirect your customers to a Xendit-hosted page.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"9d94878d-a0b6-4663-8f40-bf43b1ee671b\">Payment confirmation</h4><p data-block-id=\"21ba68fc-352a-4507-bb13-f4cf1d192392\">Subscribe to Payment Link webhooks to receive real-time payment status updates.</p><p data-block-id=\"0f76d2ca-6364-4686-9fe7-653f19d6c692\"></p>","SeoTitle":"How payment links work","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Cara kerja Link Pembayaran","Slug":"how-payment-links-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mc0wblfb-orftyd-065\">Link Pembayaran menawarkan solusi sederhana tanpa kode bagi bisnis untuk mengumpulkan pembayaran dengan mudah. Produk kami meningkatkan pengalaman pembayaran bagi pelanggan Anda, menjadikannya ideal untuk bisnis yang mencari pengalaman checkout yang dioptimalkan sambil mempertahankan integrasi yang hemat biaya.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlc-7xr2ch-067\">Pilih integrasi Anda</h2><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlc-a6ck84-068\">Rangkaian Link Pembayaran kami dirancang untuk memenuhi berbagai kebutuhan bisnis. Jelajahi opsi di bawah ini untuk menemukan salah satu yang paling cocok untuk Anda:</p><div><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"900\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:900px;width:900px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmld-k6gow4-069\"><strong>Hasil</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmld-3zircz-070\"><strong>Link Pembayaran Tunggal</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmld-b8oril-071\"><strong>Link Pembayaran Ganda</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmld-ksmrui-072\"><strong>Link Pembayaran Batch</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmld-1bn2lr-073\">Deskripsi</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmle-tsfm9i-074\">Satu link pembayaran untuk menerima satu pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmle-2fvhlw-075\">Satu link pembayaran untuk menerima beberapa pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmle-7porp1-076\">Buat beberapa link pembayaran secara massal menggunakan file CSV</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmle-2zyjna-077\">Solusi tanpa kode</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmle-016p5t-078\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmle-rv7kdw-079\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlf-lqho27-080\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlf-edyld4-081\">Integrasi API</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlf-lst1nl-082\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlf-5pef08-083\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">❌</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlf-524xci-084\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">❌</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlf-2yg884-085\">Jumlah yang dibutuhkan</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-9gj0uo-086\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-7mqpo8-087\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">❌</emoji> (opsional—pengguna akhir dapat menentukan jumlah di UI Checkout kami)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-b7mqn8-088\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">✅</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-ejlikx-089\">Kasus penggunaan terbaik</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-vwh3x0-090\">Pembayaran satu kali (misalnya, pesanan e-commerce)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-5b3nnw-091\">Buka link statis untuk beberapa pembayaran (misalnya, donasi, penggalangan dana)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-z5rf1p-092\">Faktur massal, mengatur pembayaran untuk banyak pelanggan</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlg-mlvd5p-093\"><em>Antarmuka pengguna aktual untuk referensi</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlh-uwj74e-094\"><img data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlh-vsbyme-095\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(18).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(18).png\" width=\"902\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:902px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlh-pbpue7-096\">Solusi</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlh-b5fot5-097\">Solusi tanpa kode</h3><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlh-1sssb9-098\">Dengan menggunakan antarmuka terpandu sederhana di Dasbor Xendit, Anda dapat membuat link pembayaran tanpa pengetahuan teknis apa pun. Xendit juga mendukung pengiriman link pembayaran melalui email dan WhatsApp kepada pelanggan Anda. Atau, Anda dapat membagikan link ini melalui channel komunikasi pilihan Anda.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlh-pte2i9-099\">Ikuti langkah-langkah berikut untuk membuat link Pembayaran menggunakan Dasbor Xendit:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-i7c7z2-100\" start=\"1\"><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-yovlvc-101\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-1pyqo8-102\">Buka halaman <strong>Link Pembayaran</strong> di dasbor Anda</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-fg7uyi-103\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-u5w8tt-104\">Klik <strong>Buat Link Pembayaran</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-4opc4b-105\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-23ud9a-106\">Isi <strong>detail pembayaran</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-5prkku-107\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-oeqw75-108\">(Opsional) Kosongkan jumlah untuk donasi atau beberapa link pembayaran</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-54b0qc-109\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-e8t8z6-110\">(Opsional) Mengonfigurasi detail pelanggan dan channel pemberitahuan</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-juh4bt-111\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-55nh4s-112\">Klik <strong>Buat Link Pembayaran</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-qg1png-113\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-o7lka5-114\"><strong>Bagikan link</strong> dengan pelanggan Anda untuk mengarahkan mereka ke halaman checkout yang dihosting Xendit</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-354e5p-115\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-d9pzh7-116\">Pantau pembayaran melalui notifikasi email atau buat laporan untuk pembaruan status</p></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-ui1djo-117\">Integrasi API</h3><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-ty9g6v-118\">Jika Anda memiliki kasus penggunaan yang lebih kompleks yang mengharuskan sistem Anda membuat link pembayaran secara dinamis, produk kami juga tersedia melalui integrasi berbasis API. Metode integrasi ini memungkinkan Anda menyinkronkan sistem manajemen pesanan Anda ke sistem penagihan pembayaran yang dihosting kami. <a href=\"/v1/docs/id/payment-links-api-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">You can find our detailed integration guides here</a>.   </p><h4 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-sodwbg-119\">Cara kerjanya</h4><h4 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-8f5fhg-120\">Endpoint</h4><ol data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-koxzds-121\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-93l786-122\"><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-dixgp6-123\"><code>v2/invoices</code> - untuk membuat link pembayaran dengan baris kode minimal.</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-mu2fqp-124\">Membuat link pembayaran</h4><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmli-2tc1ho-125\">Contoh payload permintaan API:</p><pre data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlj-dcc1p7-126\" language=\"json\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{  \"external_id\": \"payment-link-example\",\n  \"amount\": 100000,\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Air Conditioner\",\n      \"quantity\": 1,\n      \"price\": 100000,\n      \"category\": \"Electronic\",\n      \"url\": \"https://yourcompany.com/example_item\"\n    }\n  ]\n}</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlj-nd3fmy-127\">Respons API menyertakan URL yang dapat Anda gunakan untuk mengarahkan pelanggan Anda ke halaman yang dihosting Xendit.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlj-88tx8l-128\">Konfirmasi pembayaran</h4><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlj-2p2ymb-129\">Berlangganan webhook link Pembayaran untuk menerima pembaruan status pembayaran secara real-time.</p><p data-block-id=\"mc0wbmlj-jhx050-130\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Cara kerja Link Pembayaran","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"วิธีการทำงานของ Payment Link","Slug":"how-payment-links-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"e1512a76-7ca5-4d5b-a248-afb55369799c\">Payment Links นำเสนอโซลูชันที่ง่ายและไม่ต้องใช้โค้ด (no-code) สำหรับธุรกิจในการเก็บเงินได้อย่างง่ายดาย ผลิตภัณฑ์ของเราช่วยยกระดับประสบการณ์การชำระเงินสำหรับลูกค้าของคุณ ทำให้เหมาะสำหรับธุรกิจที่ต้องการประสบการณ์การชำระเงินที่เหมาะสมที่สุด (optimized checkout experience) ในขณะที่ยังคงรักษาการผสานรวมที่คุ้มค่า (cost-effective integration)</p><h2 data-block-id=\"0e5dce03-d6ab-4871-9a85-453a725253cc\">เลือกวิธีการผสานรวมของคุณ</h2><p data-block-id=\"0ef92717-10c2-428b-97c8-a776177fd045\">ชุดผลิตภัณฑ์ Payment Links ของเราได้รับการออกแบบมาเพื่อตอบสนองความต้องการทางธุรกิจที่หลากหลาย สำรวจตัวเลือกด้านล่างเพื่อค้นหาสิ่งที่เหมาะสมกับคุณที่สุด:</p><div><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"900\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:900px;width:900px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"d156658e-29ef-4bdc-839c-7ca439ff0f91\"><strong>ผลิตภัณฑ์</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"18665de3-85bc-4a82-a88a-a0f128a3fc9b\"><strong>Single Payment Link</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"9bdc00f3-1920-4bc4-aa7e-cd0c06acdc95\"><strong>Multiple Payment Link</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"201c7277-7009-42c7-9672-5fc150391cd9\"><strong>Batch Payment Link</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"d37ef955-6f6a-49d6-9a2d-7d10e5be04b3\">คำอธิบาย</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"b3aea85d-0eb2-4f5c-b74f-9652ee969e0b\">ลิงก์ชำระเงินเดียวสำหรับรับการชำระเงินครั้งเดียว</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1e89b412-0444-4013-b35e-81fbecf3c262\">ลิงก์ชำระเงินเดียวสำหรับรับการชำระเงินหลายครั้ง</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"ff168aff-c974-4cfc-9569-6b9f1cd4b0cc\">สร้าง Payment Link หลายรายการพร้อมกันเป็นชุดโดยใช้ไฟล์ CSV</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"a1f48ea1-350d-4820-908e-0c188b3c83fa\">โซลูชันแบบไม่ต้องใช้โค้ด (No-code solution)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"081cd5e7-cd58-4746-b15e-28c9fd62480a\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c1897ed7-ad05-475b-b598-72fdd7e92c58\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"3455b9df-d499-433b-ba90-4fd9717f2fbd\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1ff6ab41-6f3c-4c30-8373-49509e49eb9d\">การผสานรวม API</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"f679890d-4875-4961-b033-a6b617aba86f\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"164eb021-be3c-4528-aafa-7460d7c71b0f\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"77cfea66-bb2e-4fa0-a51c-6138bf18735d\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"e1686b83-4a3c-4b41-a551-aa93d2c36c67\">ต้องระบุจำนวนเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"ee610c07-e636-4ee8-a714-cb121be7ef39\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"27e5c9cb-8437-41c8-84bc-30ffe3f6d4f8\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji> (ทางเลือก—ผู้ใช้ปลายทางสามารถกำหนดจำนวนเงินได้บน Checkout UI ของเรา)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"06add090-f054-47f1-9657-4c6006b71cdc\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"8b88a567-5028-497c-903c-ab41bafeeef7\">กรณีการใช้งานที่ดีที่สุด</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"19c3bb38-39da-45a5-a262-11fe7c006e1c\">การชำระเงินครั้งเดียว (เช่น คำสั่งซื้ออีคอมเมิร์ซ)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"e6a9ea8b-38cd-4211-a889-ac1beab42729\">ลิงก์แบบคงที่ที่เปิดรับการชำระเงินหลายครั้ง (เช่น การบริจาค การระดมทุน)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"449ae556-1d3f-4e5a-a6cd-860f657db176\">การออก Invoice เป็นชุด, การจัดการการชำระเงินสำหรับลูกค้าหลายราย</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p data-block-id=\"a47fe000-71d7-42bd-98fc-ea9df48f05c0\"><em>หน้าจอผู้ใช้งานจริงสำหรับอ้างอิง</em></p><p data-block-id=\"ee8a3f7d-165d-4e01-9908-70d8145a1e73\"><img data-block-id=\"7c6f058b-a6e7-487f-aea3-9e4d8c3ff754\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(18).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(18).png\" width=\"902\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link newtab style=\"width:902px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"0ce1e7f3-705b-439d-b98f-9ed60cd190ca\">โซลูชัน</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"4c5bb93d-cfc7-4e4e-b0a9-d717479bfa7f\">โซลูชันแบบไม่ต้องใช้โค้ด (No-code solution)</h3><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"08bbccdf-ccd7-422f-b826-a2bd93b8d44d\">การใช้หน้าจอที่ใช้งานง่ายบน Xendit Dashboard ช่วยให้คุณสามารถสร้าง Payment Link ได้โดยไม่ต้องมีความรู้ด้านเทคนิค Xendit ยังรองรับการส่ง Payment Link ผ่านอีเมลและ WhatsApp ไปยังลูกค้าของคุณ หรือคุณสามารถแชร์ลิงก์เหล่านี้ผ่านช่องทางการสื่อสารใด ๆ ที่คุณเลือกได้</p><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c11bda4f-32c6-4130-bb86-24fa26b2aa5d\">ทำตามขั้นตอนเหล่านี้เพื่อสร้าง Payment Link โดยใช้ Xendit Dashboard:</p><ol data-block-id=\"4ef2203e-0eb7-42bb-a2c1-6519929cfd26\" start=\"1\"><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c7a5022d-adf6-4c2a-964a-dbc59eb0f434\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c7c46c3a-7e2d-419f-b5cc-78f18a99589b\">ไปที่หน้า <strong>Payment Links</strong> บนแดชบอร์ดของคุณ</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c8f5551f-1dcc-4edb-82e8-6c2d7651ae16\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"63669e41-9203-453e-b2f6-3f0dd3374789\">คลิก <strong>Create Payment Link</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"14ab08ce-d02e-448a-95f9-47b4ca1fed3a\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"72ba3b23-b9e7-4a23-ba6d-e6b1266b5791\">กรอก <strong>รายละเอียดการชำระเงิน</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"468e0f44-a891-4d39-a1fa-05b3441d4af9\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"dbfc4944-cb39-4d7e-b14d-143bfc6f7995\">(ทางเลือก) เว้นจำนวนเงินว่างไว้สำหรับการบริจาคหรือ Multiple Payment Link</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1c2fd757-e039-441b-9fa6-506062b74015\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1a870861-d2de-49c3-910f-4191e105e54e\">(ทางเลือก) กำหนดค่ารายละเอียดลูกค้าและช่องทางการแจ้งเตือน</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"39e5a41a-a45d-489e-9f66-31662ad01afe\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c3e5403f-8b4e-4eb5-8e52-43f50381f53d\">คลิก <strong>Create Payment Link</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"42c2f66d-1f37-4442-b676-872da50e3d82\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"3b80d47d-d361-4b31-9ea7-e736a4fb2e57\"><strong>แชร์ลิงก์</strong> กับลูกค้าของคุณเพื่อนำพวกเขาไปยังหน้าชำระเงินที่โฮสต์โดย Xendit</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"9a9218c5-dc6c-4eb6-94b9-e8596ad1e2cf\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"a23c52ca-c410-4362-bfa1-ac568358f6e5\">ติดตามการชำระเงินผ่านการแจ้งเตือนทางอีเมล หรือสร้างรายงานเพื่อดูสถานะล่าสุด</p></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"387e6a7a-9df3-45aa-8232-f9e690f1753f\">การผสานรวม API</h3><p data-block-id=\"c120054d-f922-42b0-8901-bb0d9be7eff2\">หากคุณมีกรณีการใช้งานที่ซับซ้อนมากขึ้นซึ่งระบบของคุณจำเป็นต้องสร้าง Payment Link แบบไดนามิก ผลิตภัณฑ์ของเราก็มีให้ใช้งานผ่านการผสานรวมแบบ API ด้วย วิธีการผสานรวมนี้ช่วยให้คุณสามารถซิงค์ระบบจัดการคำสั่งซื้อของคุณเข้ากับระบบเก็บเงินที่โฮสต์โดยเรา <a href=\"/v1/docs/payment-links-api-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">คุณสามารถดูคู่มือการผสานรวมโดยละเอียดของเราได้ที่นี่</a>   </p><h4 data-block-id=\"71e69fd0-833e-4aca-8f52-c7e4ae39972e\">วิธีการทำงาน</h4><h4 data-block-id=\"fad075e9-7dbe-4fcc-897c-31124a5d31d9\">Endpoints</h4><ol data-block-id=\"1324f69f-7fd8-4fc2-96d8-c9e83682b04b\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"777546fd-fd58-418d-9a01-cafd85b3920e\"><p data-block-id=\"bd93ab85-0735-48b2-b3b2-c5c8dad1f107\"><code>v2/invoices</code> - เพื่อสร้าง Payment Link ด้วยโค้ดเพียงไม่กี่บรรทัด</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"b6b5de88-efa9-432a-9a94-48a2a6cf48fb\">การสร้าง Payment Link</h4><p data-block-id=\"f3770f52-937a-4449-bc1b-db4d196ed70d\">ตัวอย่าง payload คำขอ API:</p><pre data-block-id=\"2d80317b-6930-4713-b504-f590b13498d5\" language=\"json\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{  &quot;external_id&quot;: &quot;payment-link-example&quot;,\n  &quot;amount&quot;: 100000,\n  &quot;items&quot;: [\n    {\n      &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Air Conditioner&quot;,\n      &quot;quantity&quot;: 1,\n      &quot;price&quot;: 100000,\n      &quot;category&quot;: &quot;Electronic&quot;,\n      &quot;url&quot;: &quot;https://yourcompany.com/example_item&quot;\n    }\n  ]\n}</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"caf6e6c8-4c08-40b0-85f9-03548fb22964\">การตอบกลับของ API จะมี URL ที่คุณสามารถใช้เพื่อเปลี่ยนเส้นทางลูกค้าของคุณไปยังหน้าเว็บที่โฮสต์โดย Xendit</p><h4 data-block-id=\"9d94878d-a0b6-4663-8f40-bf43b1ee671b\">การยืนยันการชำระเงิน</h4><p data-block-id=\"21ba68fc-352a-4507-bb13-f4cf1d192392\">สมัครรับ Payment Link webhooks เพื่อรับการอัปเดตสถานะการชำระเงินแบบเรียลไทม์</p><p data-block-id=\"0f76d2ca-6364-4686-9fe7-653f19d6c692\"></p>","SeoTitle":"วิธีการทำงานของ Payment Link","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Cómo funcionan los Payment Link","Slug":"how-payment-links-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"e1512a76-7ca5-4d5b-a248-afb55369799c\">Los Payment Links ofrecen una solución simple y sin código (no-code) para que los comercios cobren pagos con facilidad. Nuestro producto mejora la experiencia de pago para sus clientes, haciéndolos ideales para comercios que buscan una experiencia de checkout optimizada mientras mantienen una integración rentable.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"0e5dce03-d6ab-4871-9a85-453a725253cc\">Elija su integración</h2><p data-block-id=\"0ef92717-10c2-428b-97c8-a776177fd045\">Nuestra suite de Payment Links está diseñada para satisfacer diversos requisitos comerciales. Explore las opciones a continuación para encontrar la que mejor se adapte a usted:</p><div><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"900\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:900px;width:900px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"><col style=\"width:225px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"d156658e-29ef-4bdc-839c-7ca439ff0f91\"><strong>Producto</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"18665de3-85bc-4a82-a88a-a0f128a3fc9b\"><strong>Single Payment Link</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"9bdc00f3-1920-4bc4-aa7e-cd0c06acdc95\"><strong>Multiple Payment Link</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"201c7277-7009-42c7-9672-5fc150391cd9\"><strong>Batch Payment Link</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"d37ef955-6f6a-49d6-9a2d-7d10e5be04b3\">Descripción</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"b3aea85d-0eb2-4f5c-b74f-9652ee969e0b\">Un Payment Link para aceptar un solo pago</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1e89b412-0444-4013-b35e-81fbecf3c262\">Un Payment Link para aceptar múltiples pagos</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"ff168aff-c974-4cfc-9569-6b9f1cd4b0cc\">Cree múltiples Payment Links de forma masiva utilizando un archivo CSV</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"a1f48ea1-350d-4820-908e-0c188b3c83fa\">Solución sin código (No-code)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"081cd5e7-cd58-4746-b15e-28c9fd62480a\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c1897ed7-ad05-475b-b598-72fdd7e92c58\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"3455b9df-d499-433b-ba90-4fd9717f2fbd\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1ff6ab41-6f3c-4c30-8373-49509e49eb9d\">Integración API</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"f679890d-4875-4961-b033-a6b617aba86f\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"164eb021-be3c-4528-aafa-7460d7c71b0f\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"77cfea66-bb2e-4fa0-a51c-6138bf18735d\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"e1686b83-4a3c-4b41-a551-aa93d2c36c67\">Monto requerido</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"ee610c07-e636-4ee8-a714-cb121be7ef39\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"27e5c9cb-8437-41c8-84bc-30ffe3f6d4f8\"><emoji data-name=\"x\" title=\"cross mark\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x274c;</emoji> (opcional—el usuario final puede definir el monto en nuestra interfaz de usuario de Checkout)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"06add090-f054-47f1-9657-4c6006b71cdc\"><emoji data-name=\"white_check_mark\" title=\"check mark button\" data-unicode-version=\"6.0\">&#x2705;</emoji></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"8b88a567-5028-497c-903c-ab41bafeeef7\">Mejor caso de uso</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"19c3bb38-39da-45a5-a262-11fe7c006e1c\">Pagos únicos (por ejemplo, pedidos de e-commerce)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"e6a9ea8b-38cd-4211-a889-ac1beab42729\">Link estático abierto para múltiples pagos (por ejemplo, donaciones, recaudación de fondos)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"225\"><p data-block-id=\"449ae556-1d3f-4e5a-a6cd-860f657db176\">Facturación masiva (Bulk invoicing), organización de pagos para múltiples clientes</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p data-block-id=\"a47fe000-71d7-42bd-98fc-ea9df48f05c0\"><em>Interfaz de usuario real para referencia</em></p><p data-block-id=\"ee8a3f7d-165d-4e01-9908-70d8145a1e73\"><img data-block-id=\"7c6f058b-a6e7-487f-aea3-9e4d8c3ff754\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(18).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(18).png\" width=\"902\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link newtab style=\"width:902px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"0ce1e7f3-705b-439d-b98f-9ed60cd190ca\">Soluciones</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"4c5bb93d-cfc7-4e4e-b0a9-d717479bfa7f\">Solución sin código (No-code)</h3><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"08bbccdf-ccd7-422f-b826-a2bd93b8d44d\">Utilizando una interfaz guiada simple en el Dashboard de Xendit, usted puede crear Payment Links sin necesidad de conocimientos técnicos. Xendit también admite el envío de Payment Links a través de correo electrónico y WhatsApp a sus clientes. Alternativamente, usted puede compartir estos links a través de cualquier canal de comunicación de su elección.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c11bda4f-32c6-4130-bb86-24fa26b2aa5d\">Siga estos pasos para crear un Payment Link utilizando el Dashboard de Xendit:</p><ol data-block-id=\"4ef2203e-0eb7-42bb-a2c1-6519929cfd26\" start=\"1\"><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c7a5022d-adf6-4c2a-964a-dbc59eb0f434\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c7c46c3a-7e2d-419f-b5cc-78f18a99589b\">Vaya a la página de <strong>Payment Links</strong> en su dashboard</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c8f5551f-1dcc-4edb-82e8-6c2d7651ae16\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"63669e41-9203-453e-b2f6-3f0dd3374789\">Haga clic en <strong>Create Payment Link</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"14ab08ce-d02e-448a-95f9-47b4ca1fed3a\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"72ba3b23-b9e7-4a23-ba6d-e6b1266b5791\">Rellene los <strong>detalles del pago</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"468e0f44-a891-4d39-a1fa-05b3441d4af9\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"dbfc4944-cb39-4d7e-b14d-143bfc6f7995\">(Opcional) Deje el monto en blanco para donaciones o Multiple Payment Link</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1c2fd757-e039-441b-9fa6-506062b74015\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"1a870861-d2de-49c3-910f-4191e105e54e\">(Opcional) Configure los detalles del cliente y los canales de notificación</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"39e5a41a-a45d-489e-9f66-31662ad01afe\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"c3e5403f-8b4e-4eb5-8e52-43f50381f53d\">Haga clic en <strong>Create Payment Link</strong></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"42c2f66d-1f37-4442-b676-872da50e3d82\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"3b80d47d-d361-4b31-9ea7-e736a4fb2e57\"><strong>Comparta el link</strong> con sus clientes para redirigirlos a la página de checkout alojada por Xendit</p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"9a9218c5-dc6c-4eb6-94b9-e8596ad1e2cf\"><p dir=\"ltr\" data-block-id=\"a23c52ca-c410-4362-bfa1-ac568358f6e5\">Monitoree los pagos a través de notificaciones por correo electrónico o genere un reporte para las actualizaciones de estado</p></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"387e6a7a-9df3-45aa-8232-f9e690f1753f\">Integración API</h3><p data-block-id=\"c120054d-f922-42b0-8901-bb0d9be7eff2\">Si usted tiene un caso de uso más complejo que requiere que su sistema cree Payment Links dinámicamente, nuestro producto también está disponible a través de una integración basada en API. Este método de integración le permite sincronizar su sistema de gestión de pedidos con nuestro sistema de cobro de pagos alojado. <a href=\"/v1/docs/payment-links-api-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Usted puede encontrar nuestras guías de integración detalladas aquí</a>.   </p><h4 data-block-id=\"71e69fd0-833e-4aca-8f52-c7e4ae39972e\">Cómo funciona</h4><h4 data-block-id=\"fad075e9-7dbe-4fcc-897c-31124a5d31d9\">Endpoints</h4><ol data-block-id=\"1324f69f-7fd8-4fc2-96d8-c9e83682b04b\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"777546fd-fd58-418d-9a01-cafd85b3920e\"><p data-block-id=\"bd93ab85-0735-48b2-b3b2-c5c8dad1f107\"><code>v2/invoices</code> - para generar Payment Links con líneas de código mínimas.</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"b6b5de88-efa9-432a-a94-48a2a6cf48fb\">Creación de un Payment Link</h4><p data-block-id=\"f3770f52-937a-4449-bc1b-db4d196ed70d\">Ejemplo de payload de request API:</p><pre data-block-id=\"2d80317b-6930-4713-b504-f590b13498d5\" language=\"json\" class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\" spellcheck=\"false\">{  &quot;external_id&quot;: &quot;payment-link-example&quot;,\n  &quot;amount&quot;: 100000,\n  &quot;items&quot;: [\n    {\n      &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Air Conditioner&quot;,\n      &quot;quantity&quot;: 1,\n      &quot;price&quot;: 100000,\n      &quot;category&quot;: &quot;Electronic&quot;,\n      &quot;url&quot;: &quot;https://yourcompany.com/example_item&quot;\n    }\n  ]\n}</code></pre><p data-block-id=\"caf6e6c8-4c08-40b0-85f9-03548fb22964\">La response de la API incluye una URL que usted puede usar para redirigir a sus clientes a una página alojada por Xendit.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"9d94878d-a0b6-4663-8f40-bf43b1ee671b\">Confirmación de pago</h4><p data-block-id=\"21ba68fc-352a-4507-bb13-f4cf1d192392\">Suscríbase a los webhooks de Payment Link para recibir actualizaciones de estado de pago en tiempo real.</p><p data-block-id=\"0f76d2ca-6364-4686-9fe7-653f19d6c692\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Cómo funcionan los Payment Link","Description":null}]